                            <comment id="434325" author="yujian" created="Thu, 7 Nov 2024 19:57:58 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Hi &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/ViewProfile.jspa?name=qian_wc&quot; class=&quot;user-hover&quot; rel=&quot;qian_wc&quot;&gt;qian_wc&lt;/a&gt;,&lt;br/&gt;
The test passed on master branch but failed consistently on Lustre b2_15 aarch64 and ppc64 clients.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/89e658e7-68ed-4c56-8c28-e04c4bdfc463&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/89e658e7-68ed-4c56-8c28-e04c4bdfc463&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
It seems the patches for &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-10499&quot; title=&quot;Readonly Persistent Client Cache support&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-10499&quot;&gt;LU-10499&lt;/a&gt; can fix the failure, but there are many patches missing on b2_15 branch.&lt;br/&gt;
Is there a straightforward way to fix this issue on b2_15?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
